summary: Honestly this is probably the worst mod of all time, made for those who are tired of the standard town music and would rather hear Michael Stevens saying the famous intro for about forever.
descriptionHtml:
Honestly this is probably the worst mod of all time, made for those who are tired of the standard town music and would rather hear Michael Stevens saying the famous intro for about forever.

Just install using nexus mod manager or dump Music and the ESP in your skyrim data folder
